    public class ValuePair<L extends java.lang.Comparable<? super L>,V extends java.lang.Comparable<? super V>>
extends Pair<L,V>
implements java.lang.Comparable<ValuePair<L,V>>
    A pair of two values with type parameters. This data object is useful whenever exactly two values are required for a specific task.
